This is the base package of the GUI-client.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ClientExtension
    classes implementing ClientExtension are started automaticaly when a user has successfully login into the Rapla system.
    RaplaClientExtensionPoints
    Constant Pool of basic extension points of the Rapla client.
    ServerExtension
    a class implementing server extension is started automatically when the server is up and running and connected to a data store.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    RaplaServerExtensionPoints

Package org.rapla.plugin Description

This is the base package of the GUI-client. Communication through the backend is done through the modules of org.rapla.facade package. The gui-client is normally started through the RaplaClientService. You can also plug-in your own components into the gui.
